{"tid":2022872,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZONE完美避開TWICE....","createTime":"2020-05-18T15:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T16:04:16.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"106b9c031d3c1e4ef7957ce87ae4f4ff0e8a2f25","tid":2022872,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"大家好。我們是IZ*ONE的共同經紀公司，OFF THE RECORD， Swing Entertainment。<br />\n<br />\n感謝一直愛護和支持IZ*ONE的WIZ*ONE們，告訴大家等待已久的IZ*ONE新專輯發行的消息。<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE將於6月15日發行第三迷你專輯，開始回歸活動。成員們現在正在加快專輯的最後階段，為了發現更加完美的舞台，也在努力練習舞蹈。<br />\n<br />\n為了新迷你專輯，IZ*ONE準備的各種內容將在專輯發行前按順序公開，還計劃為WIZ*ONE準備各種活動。<br />\n<br />\n為了以更加帥氣的模樣見面正在努力準備中的IZ*ONE成員們，請多多支持。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝<br />\n<br />\n冇睇頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c78cc020b33364706fe6d40355885b31806106","tid":2022872,"uid":256952,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"Izone吊打twice綽綽有餘"},{"pid":"4360bb0b7c80485b930fa67fd7b636d0157abaff","tid":2022872,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2c78cc020b33364706fe6d40355885b31806106","tid":2022872,"uid":256952,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"Izone吊打twice綽綽有餘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"遲兩星期打你老母咩ON9"},{"pid":"64b759fa745b8a5b383ca0780983a53d3fb57160","tid":2022872,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4360bb0b7c80485b930fa67fd7b636d0157abaff","tid":2022872,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2c78cc020b33364706fe6d40355885b31806106","tid":2022872,"uid":256952,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"Izone吊打twice綽綽有餘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"遲兩星期打你老母咩ON9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"咁惡做咩啫 食屎啦你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img sr